{"tid":1333191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社福界周日發起「社工受夠了」靜默遊行　「無聲吶喊表達憤怒」","createTime":"2019-07-19T15:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T15:25:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee8f9360995d61d881f14b1eaf651d7ab989fe2","tid":1333191,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"立場報道2019/7/19 &mdash; 19:51<br />\n反送中浪潮不斷，民陣周日發起遊行，下午 3 時在銅鑼灣維園出發。社福界則在當日早上 11 時進行「社工受夠了」靜默遊行，起點為灣仔修頓球場，終點是政府總部公民廣場。參加者可自備一個沙灘吹氣波或摺紙球，寓意「交番個波給林鄭」。 <br />\n<br />\n香港社會工作者總工會、社工復興運動等五個社福團體發起周日遊行「社工受夠了」。是次遊行已獲「不反對通知書」。早前林鄭月娥回應反送中自殺個案時表示：「已動員多個非政府機構提供輔導支援服務，希望減低現時社會彌漫的負面情緒」，「政府會盡所能，包括多元教育或情緒輔導上，投入更多資源，為青年解決焦慮」<br />\n<br />\n社福界認為政府一再推卸責任，拒絕回應民間訴求，並視社福界為政權失誤的「補鑊」工具。他們強調藉由靜默遊行「 以無聲吶喊表達憤怒，要求林鄭不要卸膊」。<br />\n<br />\n是次遊行歡迎現職或前社工、社福界支援職員、社工老師、社工學生及大專院校社工系參加。參加者以黑衣為記，亦可自備沙灘吹氣波或自製摺紙球，寓意「交番個波給林鄭」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A4%BE%E7%A6%8F%E7%95%8C%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7-%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%A0%E4%BA%86-%E9%9D%9C%E9%BB%98%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%84%A1%E8%81%B2%E5%90%B6%E5%96%8A%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25A6%258F%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%25BB%2598%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2590%25B6%25E5%2596%258A%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2586%25A4%25E6%2580%2592%2F&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=2abbce89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25A6%258F%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%25BB%2598%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2590%25B6%25E5%2596%258A%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2586%25A4%25E6%2580%2592%2F&h=33639241\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A4%BE%E7%A6%8F%E7%95%8C%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7-%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%A0%E4%BA%86-%E9%9D%9C%E9%BB%98%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%84%A1%E8%81%B2%E5%90%B6%E5%96%8A%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92/</a>"},{"pid":"eca2ddd156dbe21f51e55b8110c575ef25221b64","tid":1333191,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e4dc6215acd3948a882b035c86a8112747061d","tid":1333191,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"7fd20c5b5475def1ba1701429ecf4d9964a6a14b","tid":1333191,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"幾時岀嚟暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}